review:
I visited Jinal twice during my trip to Delhi. She performed 3 fillings and complete dental cleaning.
She is quite experienced and is very talented.
Also didn't recommend anything which is not required.

She replied instantly everytime I called her and her behaviour is super nice.
You feel like talking to a friend and not a doctor.
I highly recommend her.

Doctor Katira treats the patient very friendly as well as with smile on her face . The dental treatment she done for my teeth is excellent.
Dear dr, thank you for taking such good care of my dental work.

Thank you again for helping me keep my teeth in good condition.

Dr. Jinal at IPSC Hospital was friendly, *************, efficient, and gentle. I went to have my teeth cleaned, an
experience I usually dread. Dr. Jinal’s manner was warm and caring and my teeth look and feel great! I have already recommended to see Dr. Jinal to my friends and family members.

*** ** *** **** ****** ** ****** It was a great experience. All appointments were prescheduled and on time. Dr Jinal is thorough professional and took care of the complete process smoothly. Will defintely recommend Stunning dentistry to anyone having severe dental issues. Thanks
This was our first visit for my daughter(3yr)...dfntly good experience....Dr.Jinal is very friendly with kids....
I had a great experience with Dr. Jinal mam  she is very polite and very experienced and she did my root canal treatment without any pain. I am very happy with the treatment.
I want to thanks mam you treated me in a better way, very much relieved with the treatment, very helpful and dedicated.
Timely attention to the appointments, great knowledge and professionalism, has a neat hand with kids and even with adults. Even gave bonus oral care tips.
*** **** ****** **** * **** **** ************ Dr jinal was very professional. She explained very well what was doing on. I couldn’t be happier with the results.

I visited Dr. Jinal for my root canal treatment and crown. I had a great experience, she is very polite and experienced. The procedure was completely painless and smoothly done. i would recommend her for all your dental problem
